data.description: Welcome to this charming residence that caters to your family's needs by providing ample space and a versatile floor plan. With six bedrooms and four baths, this home ensures flexibility to suit your lifestyle. The well-appointed kitchen boasts granite countertops, cherry cabinets, and a pantry for your culinary needs. The first floor is adorned with large neutral tile in the kitchen and wood-look tile flooring, creating a seamless and stylish ambiance. Additionally, the first floor offers a den/office/6th bedroom with generous closet space. Venture to the second floor to discover a spacious carpeted bonus/family room, two separate bathrooms, and four secondary bedrooms along with the primary suite. The primary suite is a haven of comfort with carpet flooring, an en-suite bath, and two separate his and hers walk-in closets. Step outside to the expansive brick-paver screened lanai, where you can enjoy conservation views and the serenity of your surroundings. Located in a fantastic neighborhood with top-rated schools, this home offers a great community vibe. The easy commute to Tampa or a short drive to St Petersburg/Clearwater adds to the convenience of this wonderful residence. Don't miss the chance to make this your home sweet home! This property is tenant-occupied until 03/11/2024
